{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"119c1a22a9","title":"给李敏、李钠的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"022f1b8f1b","index":0,"year":1954,"month":7,"day":23,"articleId":"119c1a22a9"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"8374e7d770","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"119c1a22a9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李敏，毛泽东的长女，贺子珍所生，1936年生，原籍湖南湘潭，生于陕西延安。1940年从延安赴莫斯科随贺子珍一起生活。1943年开始读苏联五年制小学，1948年秋毕业。同年冬，随贺子珍从莫斯科回哈尔滨，1949年春随姨母贺怡到北京，入北京师范大学附属女子中学，后考入北京师范大学。毕业后，1959年和孔令华结婚。后在国防科委院校局、办公厅、总政所属机关工作。李钠，毛泽东的次女，江青所生。"}],"contents":[{"id":"032fcd6306","type":"title","text":"给李敏、李钠的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"119c1a22a9"},{"id":"8374e7d770","type":"paragraph","text":"李敏、李钠，我的亲爱的女儿：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"119c1a22a9"},{"id":"e837a43226","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的信都收到了，很欢喜。北戴河、秦皇岛、山海关一带是曹孟德（操）到过的地方。他不仅是政治家，也是诗人。他的码石诗是有名的，妈妈那里有古诗选本，可请妈妈教你们读。我好，勿念。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"119c1a22a9"},{"id":"adf8e952a5","type":"paragraph","text":"亲你们！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"119c1a22a9"},{"id":"61b1594849","type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"119c1a22a9"},{"id":"8df5ad350f","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年七月廿三日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"119c1a22a9"}],"page":{"id":"3c203b3b87","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"119c1a22a9","start":171,"end":171}}}},"__N_SSG":true}